sequenceDiagram
    participant DSP as Data Science Pipelines<br/>(Pipeline Orchestrator)
    participant MLMD as MLMD gRPC Server<br/>8080/TCP gRPC/HTTP2
    participant DB as MySQL/PostgreSQL<br/>3306/TCP or 5432/TCP

    Note over DSP, DB: Flow 1: Pipeline Metadata Recording

    DSP->>MLMD: PutExecution (artifact + events + contexts)<br/>gRPC/HTTP2, Optional TLS<br/>Optional mTLS Auth
    activate MLMD
    Note right of MLMD: New DB connection per RPC<br/>(no connection pooling)
    MLMD->>DB: INSERT/UPDATE execution, artifacts, events<br/>MySQL/PostgreSQL Protocol<br/>Optional SSL, Username/Password Auth
    activate DB
    DB-->>MLMD: OK (rows affected)
    deactivate DB
    MLMD-->>DSP: PutExecutionResponse<br/>(execution_id, artifact_ids)
    deactivate MLMD

    DSP->>MLMD: PutArtifacts (batch)<br/>gRPC/HTTP2
    activate MLMD
    MLMD->>DB: INSERT/UPDATE artifacts
    activate DB
    DB-->>MLMD: OK
    deactivate DB
    MLMD-->>DSP: PutArtifactsResponse (artifact_ids)
    deactivate MLMD

    DSP->>MLMD: PutEvents (input/output links)<br/>gRPC/HTTP2
    activate MLMD
    MLMD->>DB: INSERT events
    activate DB
    DB-->>MLMD: OK
    deactivate DB
    MLMD-->>DSP: PutEventsResponse
    deactivate MLMD

    Note over DSP, DB: Flow 2: Lineage Query

    participant UI as Kubeflow Pipelines UI<br/>(Lineage Visualization)

    UI->>MLMD: GetLineageSubgraph<br/>gRPC/HTTP2, Optional TLS<br/>Optional mTLS Auth
    activate MLMD
    MLMD->>DB: SELECT (graph traversal queries)<br/>MySQL/PostgreSQL Protocol<br/>Optional SSL
    activate DB
    DB-->>MLMD: Result set (nodes, edges)
    deactivate DB
    MLMD-->>UI: LineageSubgraph<br/>(artifacts, executions, contexts, events)
    deactivate MLMD

    UI->>MLMD: GetArtifactsByContext<br/>gRPC/HTTP2
    activate MLMD
    MLMD->>DB: SELECT artifacts by context_id
    activate DB
    DB-->>MLMD: Result set
    deactivate DB
    MLMD-->>UI: GetArtifactsByContextResponse
    deactivate MLMD
